RaananaTiraProject
==================

Requirements
------------

* python-twisted
* pygame


Running the game
----------------

Start the server on some machine:

    ./rtp-server

Start up to 4 clients:

    ./rtp-client player-name /path/to/driver.py

For drive modules, see the examples direcotory.

To start a race, use rtp-admin tool on any machine:

    ./rtp-admin start

To stop a race, use rtp-admin tool on any machine:

    ./rtp-admin stop

Note: Curently clients connect to localhost. To use a server on another
machine, edit rtp/common/config.py and modify the host option to the server ip
address.


Creating a tarball
------------------

    python setup.py sdist
